rAjanaMdananamita raxisu nammananavarata || 83 ||
togalu boMbegaLaMte nAlaku |
bageya nirmANadali idaroLu |
negaLadI cauShaShTi laxaNa jAtidharmadali ||
bagebageya nAmAMkitada jI |
vigaLadellavu ninna nAmadi |
jagake toruttihudu raxisu nammananavarata || 84 ||
hUDidelu maramuTTu mAMsada |
goDe carmada hodike naravina |
kUDe hiMDige bigida maneyoLAtma nIniralu ||
bIDu tolagida baLikalA suDu |
