kUla ninnoLagihudu raxisu nammananavarata || 91 ||
sattavarigalaleke tannanu hottavaru hettavagugaLu tA |
sattu hoguvaralladuLidavare marugalekinnu ||
mRtyu benninolihudu tAvi |
nnattu mADuvudenu pUrvada |
tettiganu nInIga raxisu nammananavarata || 92 ||
maNNu maNNinoLudisiralu |
maNNu goMbegaLAgi raMjisi |
maNNinAhAradali jIvava horedu upacarisi ||
maNNinali baMdhisida dehava |
maNNugUDisabeDa jnAnada |
kaNNadRShTiyannittu raxisu nammananavarata || 93 ||

bIyavAguva tanuvinali ni |
rdAyakanu nInirdu ati hiri |
dAya saMbaDisuvare nInanukUlavAgirdu ||
tAyanagalida shishuvinaMdadi |
bAyabiDuvaMtAytale ciMtA |
dAyakane biDabeDa raxisu nammananavarata || 94 ||
modalu jananariye maraNida hadana kaDeyali tiLiye nAnu |
madyasdali nere nipuNaneMbudu baLika nagegeDu ||
modalukaDe madhyagaLa ballava |
madanajanakanu nInu ninnaya |
padayugava bayasuvenu raxisu nammananavarata || 95 ||
sAravillada dehavidu ni |
ssAravAgiha tanuvinali saM |
cAriyAgiha nIniddu kaDeyali tolagi hogutali ||
dUra tappisikoMDu bariyapa |
dUra horiside jIvanadali ida |
nAru meccuvarakaTa raxisu nammananavarata || 96 ||
aMDaveraDudbhavisidavu |
brahmAMDavadaropAdiyali piM |
DAMDavesedudu sthUlakAraNa sUxmatanuvinali ||
aMDa ninnaya romakUpado |
LaMDaledavakhilAMDavidu bra |
hmAMDanAyaka nInu raxisu nammananavarata || 97 ||
oMdu dina tanuvinali naDevudu |
bhAskarasvaragaLippa |
ttoMdu sAviradAnUranu eLubhAgadali ||
baMdadanu uDucakradallige |
taMdu dhAreyanereda munikula |
vRMdahRdayanu nInu raxisu nammananavarata || 98 ||
tolaguvaru kaDekaDe tA hole |
holenuta kaLavaLisi mUtrada |
biladoLage baMdihudu kANa baride mananoMdu ||
jaladoLage muLugidare tolagadu |
holagelasavIdehadoLu nI |
nelesiralu holeyuMDe raxisu nammananavarata || 99 ||
baridahaMkAradali tatvada |
kuruha kANade ninna dAsara |
jaredu veda purANa shAstragaLodi phalavenu ||
nararu duShkarmadali mADida |
duritavaDagalu ninna nAma |
smaraNeyoMde sAku raxisu nammananavarata || 100 ||
eMjaleMjalu eMbarAnuDi |
eMjalallave vAri jalacara |
eMjalallave hAlu karuvina eMjalenisirade ||
eMjalelliyanellayuM para |
reMjalallade bere bhAvisa |
leMjaluMTe dEva raxisu nammananavarata || 101 ||
keLuvudu harikatheya keLalu |
heLuvudu haribhakti manadali |
tALuvudu hiriyadAgi ninnaya caraNaseveyali ||
ULigava mADuvudu viShayava |
hULuvudu nijamukti kAMteya |
nALuvudu kRpemADi raxisu nammananavarata || 102 ||
I teredoLaccutana nAmada |
nUtanadi vasudhAtaladi vi |
khyAti bayasade baNNiside bhAminiya vRtadali tAnu ||
nItikovidarAlisuvadati |
prItiyali keLdavarige asurA |
rAti cennigarAya sukhagaLanIvananavarata || 103 ||
bAdarAyaNa peLda bhAratakAdikartanu dAra shrIpura |
dAdi keshavamUrtigaMkitavAda cariteyanu ||
mediniyoLidanAru hRdayado |
