yAdimUruti varapurAdhipanolivananavarata || 104 ||
kulagirigaLanvayava dhAriNi jalada pAvaka maruta jala nabha |
jalajasakha shItAMshu tAregaLuLLa pariyaMta ||
calaneyillade ninna cariteyu |
olidu dhareyoLagoppuvaMdadi |
caluva cennigarAya raxisu nammananavarata || 105 ||
nUrukanyAdAnavanu bhA |
gIrathisnAnavanu mige kai |
yAra govgaLa premadiMdali bhUsurarigolidu ||
UrugaLanUragrahArava |
dhAreyeradittaMte phala kai |
seruvudu haribhaktisArada katheya keLdavarige || 106 ||
meru maMdaranibhasuvarNava vAri |
madhyadoLiruva avaniya |
nAriyara gAyatri pashugaLannitta phalavahudu ||
dhAruNiyoLI bhaktisArava |
nAru oduvavariganudina |
cAruvaragaLannittu raxipanAdikeshavanu || 107 ||
lokadoLagatyadhikavenisuva |
kAginelesiriyAdikeshava |
tA kRpeyoLage nuDidanu I bhaktisAravanu ||
jokeyali baredodikeLdara |
nAkuladi mAdhavanu karuNipa |
shrIkamalavallabhanu mige biDadAdikeshavanu || 108 ||
